<article class="process-card"><p class="eyebrow">02</p><h3>Planning</h3><p>Our team develops a detailed plan that outlines the logistics, timelines, and creative vision for your event or session.</p></article>
<article class="process-card"><p class="eyebrow">03</p><h3>Execution</h3><p>On the day of the event or session, our experienced photographers are on-site to capture every moment with precision and artistry.</p></article>
